        "html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"max-width:100%;padding:0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg,#1E1510);min-height:540px;display:flex;align-items:stretch\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0.18\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-fullbleed-texture.svg\" alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\" />\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 40px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:center;width:100%\">\n    <div>\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:5px 14px;border:1px solid rgba(212,168,83,0.5);border-radius:4px;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--brand,#D4A853);margin-bottom:28px\">Claude × YouTube</span>\n      <h1 style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,68px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.08;color:var(--fg,#FBF8F3);margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em\">기획을<br><span style=\"color:var(--brand,#D4A853)\">Claude에게</span><br>맡겨라</h1>\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(251,248,243,0.72);max-width:420px;margin:0 0 40px\">혼자 유튜브를 운영하는 1인 사업가를 위한 AI 기획 시스템. 아이디어 고갈 없이 콘텐츠를 계속 만드는 법을 배웁니다.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center\">\n        <a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:15px 36px;background:var(--brand,#D4A853);color:#1E1510;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.01em\">지금 시작하기</a>\n        <a href=\"#preview\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:15px 28px;border:1px solid rgba(251,248,243,0.3);color:rgba(251,248,243,0.85);font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none\">무료 맛보기</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px\">\n      <figure style=\"margin:0;background:rgba(46,34,26,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,83,0.2);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)\">\n        <blockquote style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(251,248,243,0.88);margin:0 0 16px;font-style:normal\">\"3개월째 영상을 못 올리다가 이 코스 후 매주 업로드하고 있어요. Claude 기획 루틴이 핵심이었습니다.\"</blockquote>\n        <figcaption style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--brand,#D4A853);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.05em\">— 온라인 강의 사업가, 수강 완료</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n      <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px\">\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(46,34,26,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,83,0.15);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px\">\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:var(--brand,#D4A853);margin:0 0 4px\">8주</p>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(251,248,243,0.5);margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase\">Step-by-step</p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(46,34,26,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,83,0.15);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px\">\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:var(--brand,#D4A853);margin:0 0 4px\">32+</p>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(251,248,243,0.5);margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase\">실전 프롬프트</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
